description:
As a new user
    I want to register on the website
    So that I can access the features

elements.name: End to End User Registration Flow

steps.name: I navigate to the website
I click on the login menu
I log in with valid credentials
I click on the login menu
I click on the register button
I check fields to be mandatory
I verify the title of the registration page
I fill the registration form
I verify that registration is successful
the Register response should be successful
I navigate to the website
I click on the login menu
I log in with valid credentials
I should see the "Welcome to our store" text
I should see the "Log out" menu
I log out
I should be logged out successfully
I navigate to the website
I click on the login menu
I log in with valid credentials
I hover over the Computers Menu
I click on Notebooks
I verify that I have navigated to the Notebooks Page
I choose "9" on Display dropdown
I verify that only 6 items are displayed
I check "16 GB" on Filter by attributes
I verify that only 1 item is displayed
I uncheck the "16 GB" checkbox
I verify that 6 items are displayed now
I add the second and the third item on wishlist
I verify that after every item added a notification with text: "The product has been added to your wishlist" is displayed
I click on the fourth product
I verify that the detail page for this item is open
I go back to the Notebooks Page
I add the fifth and sixth item on Shopping Cart
I verify that for the two last items added a notification with text: "The product has been added to your shopping cart" is displayed
Wishlist on Menu bar displays 2
Shopping Cart on Menu bar displays 2

elements.name: End to End Shopping Cart Page

steps.name: I navigate to the website
I click on the login menu
I log in with valid credentials
I hover over the Shopping Cart Menu
I verify that the 'Go To Cart' button is displayed
I click the 'Go To Cart' button
I verify that I have navigated to the Shopping Cart Page
I verify that the following buttons are displayed:
I verify that the prices sum for all items is equal to Total Price at the end of the page, and the price color is blue

elements.name: End To End Empty Shopping Cart

steps.name: I navigate to the website
I click on the login menu
I log in with valid credentials
I hover over the Computers Menu
I click on Notebooks
I add the fifth and sixth item on Shopping Cart
I hover over the Shopping Cart Menu
I click the 'Go To Cart' button
the first item is deleted from the shopping cart
verify that the number of elements in Shopping Cart table is decreased by 1
the Estimate Shopping button is clicked
country, state, and postal code fields are filled and Apply button is clicked
verify that the number of elements in Shopping Cart table is decreased by 1
repeat the steps until the last item is deleted
